<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Blocked</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .warning-background {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #ff000015 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, #ff000015 0%, transparent 50%);
            animation: backgroundPulse 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes backgroundPulse {
            0% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        .blocked-container {
            background: rgba(25, 25, 25, 0.95);
            padding: 3.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 
                0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
                0 0 60px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            position: relative;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            animation: containerAppear 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        @keyframes containerAppear {
            from { 
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to { 
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .danger-symbol {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            position: relative;
            border: 3px solid #ff3333;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: symbolRotate 20s linear infinite;
        }

        .danger-symbol::before {
            content: '!';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 45px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ff3333;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 51, 51, 0.5);
        }

        @keyframes symbolRotate {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff3333;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 51, 51, 0.3);
            animation: titlePulse 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes titlePulse {
            0% { opacity: 0.9; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        p {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .button-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .back-button, .support-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff3333 0%, #ff0000 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .support-button {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #ff3333;
            color: #ff3333;
        }

        .back-button:hover, .support-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .back-button:active, .support-button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .support-button:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 51, 51, 0.1);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .blocked-container {
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .button-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="warning-background"></div>
    <div class="blocked-container">
        <div class="danger-symbol"></div>
        <h1>Access Denied</h1>
        <p>Your account has been temporarily blocked due to suspicious activity. This is a security measure to protect your information. Please contact our support team for immediate assistance.</p>
        <div class="button-container">
            <button onclick="window.location.href='mailto:mursalrashikk@gmail.com'" class="support-button">Contact Support</button>
            <a href="/login" class="back-button">Return to Login</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>